                <div class="desc">
                  <h3 class="name">Nell Shamrell</h3>
                  <small class="title">Senior Developer at PhishMe</small>
                  <div class="further">
                    <a class="bio" href="#" data-toggle="popover" data-html="true" data-placement="bottom" data-content="Nell Shamrell works as a Software Development Engineer for PhishMe. She also sits on the advisory board for the University of Washington Certificate in Ruby Programming. She specializes in Ruby, Rails, Regular Expressions, and Test Driven Development. Prior to entering the world of software development, she studied and worked in the field of Theatre. The world of Theatre prepared her well for the dynamic world of creating software applications. In both, she strives to create a cohesive and extraordinary experience. In her free time she enjoys practicing the martial art Naginata.<span>Seattle, USA</span>"><span class="icon icon-info"></span>Bio</a>
                    <a class="twitter" href="http://www.twitter.com/nellshamrell" target="_blank"><span class="icon icon-twitter"></span>Twitter</a>
                    <a class="github" href="http://www.github.com/nellshamrell" target="_blank"><span class="icon icon-github"></span>GitHub</a>
