                    <a class="bio" href="#" data-toggle="popover" data-html="true" data-placement="bottom" data-content="Software developer with more than 10 years of experience in languages such as C++, Java, PHP and Perl. Currently, he works with Ruby on Rails at Globo.com. He also writes on his blog at <a href='http://blog.guilhermegarnier.com' target='_blank'>blog.guilhermegarnier.com</a>.<span>Rio de Janeiro, Brazil</span>"><span class="icon icon-info"></span>Bio</a>
                    <a class="twitter" href="http://www.twitter.com/guilhermgarnier" target="_blank"><span class="icon icon-twitter"></span>Twitter</a>
                    <a class="github" href="http://www.github.com/ggarnier" target="_blank"><span class="icon icon-github"></span>GitHub</a>
                  </div>
