            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6">
              <div class="talk">
                <h3>Distributed Architecture: Scaling Projects and Teams</h3>
                <p>A few years ago, a lot of people said that Rails did not scale. Nowadays, there are a lot of big applications in Rails that show that this is not true. But when your project grows, to which point is it worth to keep everything in a single application? <span class="ellipsis">…</span><span class="content-remainder sr-only"> In this presentation, I will show details of a service distributed architecture, highlighting the advantages and drawbacks of this approach. The case of the Globo.tv (<a href="http://globotv.globo.com" target="_blank">http://globotv.globo.com/</a>) will be presented as an example. In this project, we use this architecture to allow different teams to work together.</span></p>
