            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
              <div class="talk">
                <h3>The Ruby Minimalist Counterculture</h3>
                <p>There has always been room in the Ruby community for developers to express themselves through minimalism. They use very simple tools to solve complex problems, and in this presentation I will showcase some of those tools and elaborate on the principles guiding their design.</p>
